rmation to \\\"\"someone@example.com\\\"\": rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"warning\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-14T06:19:45.78039589Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-06,checkoutservice,checkoutservice-2,\"{\"\"message\"\":\"\"failed to send order confirmation to \\\"\"someone@example.com\\\"\": rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"warning\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-14T06:20:59.113468579Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-04,checkoutservice,checkoutservice-0,\"{\"\"message\"\":\"\"failed to send order confirmation to \\\"\"someone@example.com\\\"\": rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"warning\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-14T06:21:05.198347278Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-2", "frontend-0", "frontend-1", "checkoutservice-0", "checkoutservice-2"], "service_name": ["frontend", "checkoutservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-03", "aiops-k8s-07", "aiops-k8s-06"]}, "matched_anomaly": "The system experienced an anomaly from 2025-06-14T06:10:30Z to 2025-06-14T06:31:30Z. Please infer the possible cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-14 06:10:30+00:00 to 2025-06-14 06:31:30+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "日志收集成功，以下是从数据中提取到的异常信息：\n\n### 分析日志\n\n1. **日志关键词及错误模式识别**:\n   - 多个 `frontend` 服务日志显示 `failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.46.196:7070: i/o timeout\"`\n   - 还有部分日志显示 `failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = timed out waiting for server handshake`.\n\n2. **关键词提取**:\n   - **错误类型**: `connection error`, `timeout`, `context canceled`\n   - **日志标签**: `frontend--connection error`, `frontend--timeout`\n   - **异常模式**: `transport: Error while dialing`, `timed out waiting for server handshake` \n\n3. **嫌疑服务和故障模式识别**:\n   - 可能的 DNS 故障和网络连接超时问题。\n   - `transport: Error while dialing` 指向网络配置问题。\n   - `context canceled` 出现在 `checkoutservice` 中，可能是请求超时后导致的后续影响。\n\n### 输出 JSON\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"timeout\", \"connection error\", \"transport\", \"context canceled\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"网络连接超时，可能的 DNS 配置问题，导致 'transport: Error while dialing'\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.46.196:7070: i/o timeout\\\"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"请求被取消，可能是由于前端服务的问题导致的后续影响\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to send order confirmation to \\\"someone@example.com\\\": rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n以上是通过系统日志分析得出的可能原因。请进行后续更细致的网络和配置问题检查以验证这些假设。", "trace_analysis_findings": "在分析 UUID: 9c3b8fe7-282 的异常数据中，观察到多个显著的异常调用链。分析结果如下：\n\n### 延迟异常\n- `checkoutservice->cartservice`\n  - 在 `hipstershop.CartService/GetCart` 操作中，从正常平均耗时 8453 ms 增加到异常平均耗时 25780106 ms，两者的延迟倍数为 **3051.5**。\n  - 在 `hipstershop.CartService/EmptyCart` 操作中，从正常平均耗时 18245 ms 增加到异常平均耗时 21198510 ms，两者的延迟倍数为 **1161.6**。\n- `frontend->checkoutservice`\n  - 在 `hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder` 操作中，正常平均耗时 144331 ms 增加到异常平均耗时 27689419 ms，两者的延迟倍数为 **191.9**。\n\n### 错误传播路径\n- `checkoutservice` 在调用 `cartservice` 时出现 `connection error` 和 `timeout error`，表明 `cartservice` 的连接问题是一个主要瓶颈。\n- `frontend` 在调用 `checkoutservice` 进行 `PlaceOrder` 时，出现多次 `cart failure: failed to get user cart during checkout` 的错误，意味着 `checkoutservice` 内部调用 `cartservice` 出现问题。\n\n### 状态码分析\n- HTTP 500 状态码和确认的 `connection error` 在 `checkoutservice` 与 `cartservice` 的通信中频繁出现（n=66次）。\n- 通过 `frontend` 与 `checkoutservice` 的调用，HTTP 500 错误状态码也频繁被记录（n=109次）。\n\n综上所述，异常主要集中于 `checkoutservice` 和 `cartservice` 之间的通信问题，这些问题导致了显著的延迟以及错误传播。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"checkoutservice->cartservice\", \"rrt_max\", \"frontend->checkoutservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从正常 8,453 ms 增至异常 25,780,106 ms 延迟倍数：3051.5\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"存在多次 `connection error` 和 `timeout error`\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"从正常 144,331 ms 增至异常 27,689,419 ms 延迟倍数：191.9\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "从收集的数据中检测到以下异常调用链和指标：\n\n- **异常指标**:\n  - `error_ratio`\n  - `client_error_ratio`\n  - `server_error_ratio`\n  - `rrt`\n  - `rrt_max`\n  - `pod_cpu_usage`\n\n- **显著异常**:\n  1. **Frontend Service**:\n     - 多个实例（`frontend-0`, `frontend-1`, `frontend-2`）出现 `error_ratio` 和 `server_error_ratio` 异常，变化率高达 200% 和 53% 以上。\n     - `rrt_max` 和 `rrt` 有显著的变化，最大延迟从 274,921.5 增加到 60,001,060.0。\n  \n  2. **Cartservice**:\n     - `cartservice-0` 以及 `cartservice-1` 表现出显著的响应时间异常 (`rrt` 和 `rrt_max`)，最大延迟和平均响应时间异常增加。\n     \n  3. **Checkoutservice**:\n     - `checkoutservice-0` 和 `checkoutservice-2` 的 `rrt` 和 `rrt_max`显著增加，变化率接近 200%。\n\n  4. **Shippingservice**:\n     - `shippingservice-0` 和 `shippingservice-2` 的 `client_error_ratio` 和 `error_ratio` 显著增加，变化率达到 63.16%。\n\n  5. **Pod 指标异常**:\n     - `adservice-0` 的 `pod_cpu_usage` 异常虽然未显著增加（0.38 到 0.01），但变化率为 1.917。\n\n### 发现：\n1. **Frontend 服务压力问题**似乎是整个系统延迟增加的根源，多个实例都出现了异常。\n2. **Cartservice 和 Checkoutservice** 的响应时间异常同样严重，可能与系统前端的异常指标一致。\n3. **Shippingservice 错误率激增**，可能是由于依赖的其他系统服务异常导致。\n4. **Pod 级别异常**在 `adservice-0` 中存在轻微 CPU 使用变化，但未造成直接影响。\n\n### 输出 JSON\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"High error ratios and response time variations detected across multiple frontend instances.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Error ratio increased to ~0.29 with rrt_max peaking at 60,001,060.0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased response time metrics detected within cartservice.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max increased from 5,676.5 to 42,868,664.6 with a significant change in rrt.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant rise in rrt and rrt_max metrics.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max for checkoutservice-0 surged from 213,176.5 to 20,002,812.0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"High client and error ratios observed.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Client error ratio increased with a median change ratio indicating an anomaly (62.53 to 63.16).\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这些发现指示系统服务负载不平衡以及从属服务的连锁反应问题是潜在的原因。"}
